### Add message
GRAPHQL http://localhost:8080/graphql
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

mutation {
  addMessage(input: {content: "new message "}) {
    id,
    content
  }
}

### hello message
GRAPHQL http://localhost:8080/graphql
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

query {
  hello {
    id,
    content
  }
}

### Subscriptions over WebSockets
GRAPHQL http://localhost:8080/graphql
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

subscription  {
    messages {
         id,
        content
    }
}

